

modular extensibility

do not match underscore / underscored variables

combine constraints:

t(a,b), {
  s1(a,c) >>> ....;
  s2(a,c) >>> ....;
}


database: removing only by flagging and batch real remove;

var constraints. E.g.:

t(a,b), b(a,c) >>> ...

arguments in arrays in body (should be passed in body arguments)

functions as constraints in arguments (for higher order calls)

ensure body argument in brackets: e.g. resolve[action](id)

externalize let variables / functions

check underscored variables in body (rename?)


integrate constraints into regular objects, e.g. dom elements



